\insrsid2457556\charrsid6246232  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4990402\charrsid6246232 set and the best dinner set that only came out for great occasions, weddings, funerals and Christmas, and that sort of thing. And there was an overmante}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2457556\charrsid6246232 l, a big glass overmant}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4990402\charrsid6246232 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2457556\charrsid6246232 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4990402\charrsid6246232  over the fireplace, and later on we had a piano, 'cos, my sister, you know, they wanted her to play the piano.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14644286 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4990402\charrsid6246232 Any ornaments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8984427 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4990402\charrsid6246232 Yes, there were one or two pieces of pottery, quite large, larger than that jug there.
\par 
