\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8984427 FW  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4990402\charrsid6246232 Yes, and they were \'85 I wouldn't know the nature of them, I don't 
